nodes.text: Darita was a human female who served as a TIE fighter pilot in the Galactic Empire's 204th Imperial Fighter Wing. She was with Shadow Wing during the Battle at Chadawa and was killed during the Battle of Jakku. Her sister was Captain Darita, and one of them used the first name Shay.
Darita appeared in the 2021 novel Victory's Price, written by Alexander Freed.
